{"tid":2456732,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇格蘭（格仔Army）算唔算係歐國盃其中一大黑馬","createTime":"2021-03-22T06:56:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-26T09:14:08.000Z","uid":234509,"like":1,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"b00e886349d02ea7fafffec5a08c8fddd3c9a55f","tid":2456732,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-22T06:56:04.000Z","msg":"前中後都係相對成熟嘅一屆<br />\n龍門：是能但<br />\n<br />\n中堅：<br />\n秦亞尼，英超top2左閘，俾羅便狗迫到國家隊要打中堅<br />\n勿劏美麗，曼聯真核，跟下80m中堅打中堅屈到傻<br />\n谷巴：列斯聯隊長，鐵血<br />\n<br />\n閘位：<br />\n羅便臣，英超最茅球員，MMA 之鬼<br />\n<br />\n中場：<br />\n麥根哥：維拉真核，有佢逗住中場carry格列珠哥<br />\nRyan Christie：蘇超第一中場，好多英超隊想要<br />\n岩士唐（唐哥）：英超第一左中場<br />\n<br />\n鋒線：<br />\n賴恩費沙：有季英超助攻王，勁！<br />\n痴阿當斯：最新入籍，英超球員，勁！<br />\n<br />\n所以我今屆會支持蘇格蘭！<br />\n有人想睇我分析其他隊會再講。"},{"pid":"bd034f6aecc46e60cd24079d18be6e68f09d8c52","tid":2456732,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"推啦"},{"pid":"e8da8a5d7675461d059e22f83386213b5a66ff2a","tid":2456732,"uid":38189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"bd034f6aecc46e60cd24079d18be6e68f09d8c52","tid":2456732,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:21:35.000Z","msg":"推啦"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T06:31:38.000Z","msg":"樓主分析得幾好"},{"pid":"3ab88ab92c5bcb5421bbb0f43e260554e49efcc9","tid":2456732,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"廢撚事同你講<br />\n你真係On9"},{"pid":"cc8d6e66f1ce3eaff3e807807b91708ef0c97de6","tid":2456732,"uid":234509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3ab88ab92c5bcb5421bbb0f43e260554e49efcc9","tid":2456732,"uid":60658,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:04:03.000Z","msg":"廢撚事同你講<br />\n你真係On9"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-26T09:12:41.000Z","msg":"點解"},{"pid":"c488f22dc3f762b3c5066d19d02ce653ec0094ca","tid":2456732,"uid":52571,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"cc8d6e66f1ce3eaff